title: Rocket League sales revenue worldwide 2016
summary: This bar chart has 2 categories for the x axis representing Month, and a y axis representing Revenue in million U.S. dollars.
The highest category is found at June_2016 where Revenue in million U.S. dollars is 110.0.
The lowest category is found at December_2015 where Revenue in million U.S. dollars is 70.0.
gold: The statistic presents information on the sales revenue generated by Rocket League worldwide as of June 2016 . According to estimates , the game developed by Psyonix generated 110 million U.S. dollars in sales revenue in the presented period .
